class 5
handling Checkboxex and Radiobuttons
1. if you have only 1 Checkbox  or radiobutton - just click on it
2. if you have multiple - store in a list and loop through

Dropdowns
Drop is a menu or a method which allows a user to select one or multiple options

Types of dropdrowns
1. single select
2.multiple select

Handling a dropdown
1.just clicking on the dropdown and clicking on the option ( not recommended)
2. Using Select class
       in order to use Select class, we need to make sure we have a
       <select> tag in html

Selecting options from the dropdown can be done in 3 ways :
1. by index
2. by physical text
3. by value;

in order to deselect options we can use following methods;
deselectByValue();
deselectByIndex();
deselectByVisibleTExt();
deselectAll();